&lt;p class=&quot;article-teaser&quot;&gt;The erotic aspects of Hodgson's work have been universally and justly abused. What on earth was he trying to do?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;What was Hodgson Attempting in his Treatment of the Erotic in THE NIGHT LAND and THE HOUSE ON THE BORDERLAND?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By &lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/about/authors-and-artists/107-andy-robertson&quot;&gt;Andy Robertson&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
